The Second Grievous Compleint is Oppression;
and whether it be True or False, let it be strongly
Urg'd, and Credited, 'tis the same thing.

The Causes of it are so many, and so incertain, 'tis hard to assign particular Remedies. In some Cases, Restreint of Bu • lding i • convenient; In others,
